    h2 About us
    p Ulf and Lars Lunge have made their dream come true in a restored historic building. They produce high-tech shoes by hand. As marathon runners themselves they know exactly where shoes pinch. They are passionate about quality and sustainability.
    p Ulf and Lars Lunge wanted to invent more than just a sports shoe. Their goal was demanding: It was supposed to be a luxurious companion for sports and everyday life, not only comfortable, healthy, fitting and durable, but also leaving a good feeling and conscience. The brothers from Hamburg already knew the sports shoe market very well at the time of the foundation of their own manufactory. They were dealers for more than 30 years and are marathon runners themselves. Whether in their profession or running - time and again they discovered that there were simply no genuine quality shoes that met their own expectations.

